Sentencas: During the past decade San Diego State University (SDSU) has become an active centre for research and education in powder sintering.
Titulo: Sintering research at San Diego State University

Sentencas: The research carried out in the uinversity's Powder Technology Laboratory (PTL, www.ptl.sdsu.edu) includes the mathematical modelling of sintering processes and a broad range of projects on sintering applications such as hydrogen storage, solar cells, the development of advanced materials for solid oxide fuel cells, and the thermal management of electronic circuitry.
Titulo: Sintering research at San Diego State University
